# Mission Control — Hook Installation
# Records installing hooks into Claude Code settings

Output docs/tapes/install.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1000
Set Height 500
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 40ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 0.5

Type "npx tsx src/index.ts install"
Enter
Sleep 4s

Sleep 2s
